<br />\n<br />\nOptus and Vodafone declined to name which domains they blocked but the same platforms also failed to load on their networks on Tuesday afternoon.<br />\n<br />\nThe ban on 4chan was lifted a few hours later.<br />\n<br />\nVodafone said while blocking requests normally came from the courts or law enforcement agencies &quot;this was an extreme case which we think requires an extraordinary response&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;While there were discussions at an industry level about this issue, this is a decision Vodafone Australia came to independently,&quot; a spokeswoman said in a statement.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We understand this may inconvenience some legitimate users of these sites, but these are extreme circumstances and we feel this is the right thing to do,&quot; Telstra networks and IT executive Nikos Katinakis said in a statement."},{"pid":"9e08f72bf36c1846548f2f7d827e9bd2b7e15b6e","tid":1068101,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"878ecb269fd53ed5c2cba96f390100c72c78badc","tid":1068101,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4091598a8881e66af4d57cc71dc80b124a4f4bea","tid":1068101,"uid":152825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76d31cd48868e2967dfa3d4d82a1c47d4c2319f1","tid":1068101,"uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"我今朝WTAPP仲收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"求片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:47:57.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">magnet:?xt=urn:btih:040faf179d1eacb0659ff96a85a421100533c66d&amp;dn=Christchurch%20Shooting&amp;tr=http%3a%2f%2ftracker3.itzmx.com%3a6961%2fannounce&amp;tr=http%3a%2f%2ftracker.kiwifarms.net%3a8000%2fannounce&amp;tr=udp%3a%2f%2fexodus.desync.com%3a6969%2fannounce&amp;tr=udp%3a%2f%2f9.rarbg.to%3a2710%2fannounce&amp;tr=udp%3a%2f%2fthetracker.org%3a80%2fannounce&amp;tr=udp%3a%2f%2ftracker.coppersurfer.tk%3a6969%2fannounce&amp;tr=udp%3a%2f%2ftracker.opentrack